The evidence with the title 'Donald Trump: Grover Norquist says he's fiscal conservative | time ' says Jun 3, 2016  ... Americans For Tax Reform president Grover Norquist says Donald Trump would be the most fiscally conservative president since Ronald Reagan .  ... He 'd “ borrow knowing that if the economy crashed you could make a deal ” which many interpret to mean he'd be willing to deficit spend economic stimulus. 
